	Document(content="""Note: <p>Dear Students,<br />The Mini Project grades have been finalized and are now available for viewing on both Brightspace and Gradescope platforms. It is essential that you take a moment to carefully review your grades and verify that they have been accurately transferred to Brightspace, as the final <strong>Brightspace score will ultimately determine your grading for this assignment.</strong><br /><br />If you encounter a &#39;0&#39; grade on your Brightspace account, it may be attributable to one of the following reasons:<br />1. Your report was not submitted on Gradescope, or<br />2. The Google form indicating your team details was not completed.<br /><br /></p><p>Please be aware that in instances where both team members submitted the report on Gradescope, we have solely graded one person&#39;s report to avoid duplication.<br /><br />In the event that you received an extension approved by the instructor and still find your Mini Project grade has been penalized, kindly submit a regrade request. Likewise, if you experience any other discrepancies with your grade, such as a mismatch between the scores on Gradescope and Brightspace, you are encouraged to send a regrade request to <a href='mailto:ece20875.purdue.university@gmail.com' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>ece20875.purdue.university@gmail.com</a>. Your email should include the following information:<br /><br />Subject: Mini Project Regrade.<br /><br />Body:<br />Section Number<br />Grading item (e.g., Mini Project)<br />Purdue email (if not sent from a Purdue email)<br />A clear and concise explanation for the regrade, including specific details and evidence to support your justification.<br /><br /></p><p>Kindly note that the regrade request window will remain open for a <strong>limited period of 24 hours only</strong>. To ensure that your request is duly considered, please submit it within the specified time frame. If you have any questions or concerns, do not hesitate to reach out to the course staff via Piazza.<br /><br /></p><p>Best,<br />Gaurav Patel</p>""", meta={'folders': ['project'], 'title': 'IMPORTANT: Mini Project Grades Now Available - Please Verify', 'timestamp': '2023-05-07T16:30:20Z', 'user': 'kskmx82xa2s4ad', 'tags': ['instructor-note', 'project'], 'likes': 4, 'views': 158}),
