	Document(content="""Question: <p>Hi I&#39;m running into an error with my kmeans function. and I&#39;m not sure what&#39;s wrong. This is my code:</p><div><div>points = makePointList(point_data)</div><div>clusters = createClusters(cluster_data)</div></div><div><div>for pnt in points:</div><div>    check = pnt.moveToCluster(pnt.closest(clusters))</div><div>for cluster in clusters:</div><div>    cluster.updateCenter()</div><div></div></div><p>This is my output:</p><p>Cluster: 0 points and center = [0. 0.]<br />Cluster: 7 points and center = [4.185714285714286, -0.1857142857142857]<br />   [-0.5  3. ]<br />   [11.  -4.5]<br />   [0.  1.2]<br />   [ 8. -3.]<br />   [0.3 4.5]<br />   [0.5 2.5]<br />   [10. -5.]</p> Answer: <p>Right now, you are updating the centers for all the clusters once the points are moved to their closest clusters. However, as the hint in the comments says, you would have to keep moving points to their closest clusters and updating the centers of all clusters until no more points are moved. I would suggest thinking about the hint and seeing how you might reflect that in the code.</p>""", meta={'folders': ['hw9'], 'title': 'Error with kmeans function', 'timestamp': '2023-04-08T22:58:37Z', 'user': 'k0by7b3lf0a6s3', 'tags': ['hw9', 'student'], 'likes': 0, 'views': 14}),
	Document(content="""Question: <p><img src='/redirect/s3?bucket=uploads&amp;prefix=paste%2Fktnb5b8oexj1jg%2F9cf309044ec36a8819ea0a77ecadc04426d53350f8242f2c06477fa20bc84fdc%2Fimage.png' alt='image.png' /></p><p>I am curious what @property does.</p> Answer: <p>It’s a decorator.</p><p></p><p><a href='https://docs.python.org/3/library/functions.html#property' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>https://docs.python.org/3/library/functions.html#property</a></p><p></p><p>For more on decorators, see for example<br /><a href='https://realpython.com/primer-on-python-decorators/' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>https://realpython.com/primer-on-python-decorators/</a></p><p></p><p>It’s worth noting that we are not teaching decorators in this course.</p><p></p>""", meta={'folders': ['hw9'], 'title': 'What does @property do?', 'timestamp': '2023-04-08T19:11:37Z', 'user': '', 'tags': ['hw9', 'student'], 'likes': 0, 'views': 144}),
