	Document(content="""Question: <p>my compare langs function keeps returning a null string because the intersection function does not find any similarities between any of the lang files. I am wondering what I am doing wrong. Could I get some di<img src='/redirect/s3?bucket=uploads&amp;prefix=paste%2Fktnb5gx345d2ba%2Fdbfc5b4ec9a4039c1dfc1331c67154f163f17e11975c3c61daa76933744935a2%2FScreen_Shot_2023-03-25_at_9.57.33_PM.png' alt='Screen_Shot_2023-03-25_at_9.57.33_PM.pngNaN' />rection?</p> Answer: <p>You seem to be iterating with i on langFiles and indexing it with j in the loop. Try to get common n-gram counts between each file in langFiles and the test_file, and return then language with the largest common count.</p>""", meta={'folders': ['hw8'], 'title': 'hw8 compare langs function advice', 'timestamp': '2023-03-26T02:00:38Z', 'user': 'ktnb5gx345d2ba', 'tags': ['hw8', 'student'], 'likes': 0, 'views': 10}),
