	Document(content="""Question: <p>I&#39;m using scholar for my code, so I&#39;ve just been editing the writeup on my local computer, but the end of the directions says to push the completed writeup along with our code. Do we need to do this or is it fine to just upload it to gradescope?</p><p></p><p><img src='/redirect/s3?bucket=uploads&amp;prefix=paste%2Fktnb4yplxsk7g3%2Fc61970fa4d503418e159669f4c607451e66539f61da62993cbda92b7f327dfa7%2Fimage.png' alt='image.pngNaN' width='864' height='146' /></p> Answer: <p>You could do it to be safe, I am sure you won&#39;t be penalized for having it on Github.</p>""", meta={'folders': ['hw7'], 'title': 'Do we have to push the writeup to GitHub too?', 'timestamp': '2023-03-24T17:57:16Z', 'user': '', 'tags': ['hw7', 'student'], 'likes': 0, 'views': 102}),
	Document(content="""Note: <p>Hi Class!<br style='font-style:normal;font-weight:400' />Homework 8 has been released on GitHub classroom. Please use the link in the post to accept the assignment and get started with the homework for the course. Note that Homework 8 is due on the 31st of March at 11:59pm. Moreover, you can also take benefit of the TA lab hours (in-person and virtual) to get help for the current and all future homeworks.<br /><br />Homework 8: <a target='_blank' href='https://classroom.github.com/a/LWPrUfVt' style='text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;font-weight:400' rel='noopener noreferrer'>https://classroom.github.com/a/LWPrUfVt</a><br /><br />Following the link, you will get access to the homework. The homework will provide instructions on how to submit the homework. <br /><br /><strong>Note:</strong> <b style='font-style:normal'>Use the same GitHub account that you documented in the GitHub user google form survey we shared at the beginning of the class.<br /><br /></b>TA Lab Hours Info:<br style='font-style:normal;font-weight:400' />Virtual lab hours (Discord): T-F 9-11 am ET, 1-2 pm ET, and 5-8 pm ET. Discord link: <b style='font-style:normal'><a target='_blank' href='https://discord.gg/vU94QaeacS' style='text-decoration:none' rel='noopener noreferrer'>https://discord.gg/vU94QaeacS</a></b><br style='font-style:normal;font-weight:400' />Limited in-person lab hours (maximum of 10 people per half hour slot) :<br style='font-style:normal;font-weight:400' />BHEE 206 (primary - go here first) &amp; 207 (overflow) T-F 5pm-8pm ET</p>""", meta={'folders': ['hw8'], 'title': 'Homework 8 Released!', 'timestamp': '2023-03-24T16:03:53Z', 'user': 'kskmx82xa2s4ad', 'tags': ['hw8', 'instructor-note'], 'likes': 1, 'views': 289}),
