	Document(content="""Question: <p>For hw7, when pushing the code to github, which formats are we supposed to submit?</p><p></p><p>- for polyfit.py, should I submit it with degrees set to [2,4] or [1,2,3,4,5,6]?</p><p>- for regularize-cv.py, should I submit it with the test case lmbda = [1, 100, 1200, 3000] commented or uncommented?</p><p></p><p>Thanks</p> Answer: <p>I believe for regularize-cv.py the test case should be commented out. Also, I believe degrees should be [1,2,3,4,5,6]</p>""", meta={'folders': ['hw7'], 'title': 'HW7 Submission Format', 'timestamp': '2023-03-23T14:51:51Z', 'user': '', 'tags': ['hw7', 'student'], 'likes': 0, 'views': 130}),
