	Document(content="""Question: <p>I have an expression that&#39;s working correctly in the regex101 checker but in Python I don&#39;t get a match. What&#39;s the issue here?</p><p><img src='/redirect/s3?bucket=uploads&amp;prefix=paste%2Fl6mapszwts17od%2Fbf0dfd557d0f9cafeee9d3a422843ffcc73584551ae1588386a4ffafb0a23bb4%2Fregex.png' width='939' height='180' alt='' /></p><p><img src='/redirect/s3?bucket=uploads&amp;prefix=paste%2Fl6mapszwts17od%2Fc1d19e509cb0b640b40e8d32ffa5aca5bf2dcbc1f12b4c5a423b7ccb990bf1cf%2Fpythonreg.png' width='872' height='697' alt='' /></p> Answer: <p>Figured it out, match only checks the beginning.</p>""", meta={'folders': ['hw6'], 'title': 'HW6 P2', 'timestamp': '2023-02-27T20:38:40Z', 'user': 'l6mapszwts17od', 'tags': ['hw6', 'student'], 'likes': 0, 'views': 13}),
