	Document(content="""Question: <p><img src='/redirect/s3?bucket=uploads&amp;prefix=paste%2Fktnb5oyje5r3kv%2F7e5474ca0d448d3e387d92cf58afd52146fcbfa083c7f71083be1f85d0c57857%2FSCR-20230225-mgf.png' width='638' height='123' alt='' /></p><p>Is the whitespace after test case 1 and 3 supposed to be there? I know that on the assignment sheet it says not return any extra spaces, which I haven&#39;t and am confused on whether or not this whitespace is considered extra spaces or not.</p> Answer: <p>When printing out the test case results, I added in the tab to make it more easy to read the results. If it says your answer is correct, you did it correctly. </p>""", meta={'folders': ['hw6'], 'title': 'Problem 3 whitespace', 'timestamp': '2023-02-25T21:13:16Z', 'user': '', 'tags': ['hw6', 'student'], 'likes': 0, 'views': 167}),
