	Document(content="""Note: <p>Hi Class!</p><p></p><p><br />Homework 5 has been released on GitHub classroom.</p><p></p><p><strong>This assignment requires part of your submission to be submitted on</strong> <strong>Gradescope! </strong>You all should have received an email from gradescope notifying you of your enrollment in the course. I also put a link under &#34;Content&#34; in Brightspace that will bring you to gradescope. <a href='https://www.gradescope.com/' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>https://www.gradescope.com</a></p><p></p><p>Please start this assignment early! This can be a challenging assignment.</p><p></p><p></p><p>Please use the link in the post to accept the assignment and get started with the first homework for the course. Note that Homework 5 is due on the 17th of February at 11:59pm. <br /><br /></p><p>Homework 5: </p><p><a href='https://classroom.github.com/a/isS6ulqu' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>https://classroom.github.com/a/isS6ulqu</a><br />*Follow the link, you will get access to the homework. The homework will provide instructions on how to submit the homework. This class does not have the students added the github classroom. <strong></strong></p><p></p><p dir='ltr'>TA Lab Hours Info:<br />Virtual lab hours (Discord): T-F 9-11 am ET, 1-2 pm ET, and 5-8 pm ET. Discord link: <a href='https://discord.gg/vU94QaeacS' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'><strong>https://discord.gg/vU94QaeacS</strong></a></p><p dir='ltr'>Limited in-person lab hours (maximum of 10 people per half hour slot) :<br />BHEE 206(primary - go here first) &amp; 207 (overflow) T-F 5pm-8pm ET </p>""", meta={'folders': ['hw5'], 'title': 'HW5 Released', 'timestamp': '2023-02-10T19:48:01Z', 'user': 'kskmxecspaq4i1', 'tags': ['hw5', 'instructor-note'], 'likes': 1, 'views': 320}),
