	Document(content="""Question: <p>The output to my problem number 2 has an extra set of brackets around the values of my dictionary. Is this output acceptable, or if not does anyone have any insight on how to remove the brackets from the dictionary values?</p><p></p><p><img src='/redirect/s3?bucket=uploads&amp;prefix=paste%2Fktnb69xvrws6s1%2F0dcc23a8c84f69abf1a2071cac32329003db90a106225c2446aaf313f0084c93%2F_1.png' width='557' height='23' alt='' /></p><p><img src='/redirect/s3?bucket=uploads&amp;prefix=paste%2Fktnb69xvrws6s1%2Fcd4af1a45de595dcce7a8816798d4046ea77c684615da4cb588a4f5fd51d3698%2F_2.png' width='547' height='26' alt='' /></p> Answer: <p>Your values should be tuples. It seems like you have a list of tuples instead. I cannot determine more without looking at the code itself.</p>""", meta={'folders': ['hw2'], 'title': 'HW2 Problem 2 output formatting', 'timestamp': '2023-01-22T18:47:52Z', 'user': '', 'tags': ['hw2', 'student'], 'likes': 0, 'views': 160}),
